      "description": "This BMW E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example of the celebrated S54-powered chassis. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features a recently serviced VANOS system and individual throttle bodies, ensuring crisp throttle response across the powerband. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced to maintain torsional rigidity. The suspension has been enhanced with Bilstein B6 dampers and polyurethane bushings for improved turn-in precision. While showing minor road-going patina, the vehicle remains structurally sound with a clean undercarriage and a driver-focused interior featuring functional Nappa leather bolsters. A superb choice for the enthusiast seeking a visceral, analog driving experience.",
